shapes3d.utils

Class C_Rod

  • java.lang.Object
    • shapes3d.utils.Contour
      • shapes3d.utils.C_Rod

  • public class C_Rod
extends Contour
    Pre-fabricated class that creates an rod (symmetrical) contour.
    There is a single constructor that allows you to specify the rod radius and the number of faces (minimum 3).
    Author:
    Peter Lager
